data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 bedroom, 1 bath bungalow, a true gem that has been completely rehabbed just over a year ago. This home combines classic bungalow charm with modern updates, making it an ideal choice for comfortable living. The exterior of the house boasts all-new siding and windows, giving it a fresh inviting curb appeal. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a beautifully renovated interior with new flooring that adds warmth and character to every room. The comprehensive rehab included updates to the electrical wiring and panel, plumbing, and even the heating and cooling system. With all these essential upgrades, you can move in with confidence and enjoy worry-free living. The kitchen is a highlight of this bungalow, featuring brand new stainless steel appliances. The modern electric water heater provides ample hot water for your convenience. The attic space holds potential for conversion to additional living space. Don't miss this opportunity for a move-in-ready home with room to grow!
